{
  "video_id": "BXlnrFpCu0c",
  "title": "My son was a Columbine shooter. This is my story | Sue Klebold",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12900.0,
      "end_time": 15396.0,
      "text": "The last time I heard my son's voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15420.0,
      "end_time": 17756.0,
      "text": "was when he walked out the front door"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17780.0,
      "end_time": 19600.0,
      "text": "on his way to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20300.0,
      "end_time": 22500.0,
      "text": "He called out one word in the darkness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23140.0,
      "end_time": 24340.0,
      "text": "\"Bye.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24820.0,
      "end_time": 27820.0,
      "text": "It was April 20, 1999."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28700.0,
      "end_time": 31756.0,
      "text": "Later that morning, at Columbine High School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31780.0,
      "end_time": 34716.0,
      "text": "my son Dylan and his friend Eric"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34740.0,
      "end_time": 37600.0,
      "text": "killed 12 students and a teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38100.0,
      "end_time": 41780.0,
      "text": "and wounded more than 20 others before taking their own lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42980.0,
      "end_time": 46350.0,
      "text": "Thirteen innocent people were killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46600.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "leaving their loved ones in a state of grief and trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50140.0,
      "end_time": 51996.0,
      "text": "Others sustained injuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52200.0,
      "end_time": 56600.0,
      "text": "some resulting in disfigurement and permanent disability."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57660.0,
      "end_time": 59476.0,
      "text": "But the enormity of the tragedy"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59500.0,
      "end_time": 63620.0,
      "text": "can't be measured only by the number of deaths and injuries that took place."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64540.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67956.0,
      "text": "There's no way to quantify the psychological damage"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67980.0,
      "end_time": 69916.0,
      "text": "of those who were in the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69940.0,
      "end_time": 73300.0,
      "text": "or who took part in rescue or cleanup efforts."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74100.0,
      "end_time": 77740.0,
      "text": "There's no way to assess the magnitude of a tragedy like Columbine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78500.0,
      "end_time": 80756.0,
      "text": "especially when it can be a blueprint"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80780.0,
      "end_time": 84220.0,
      "text": "for other shooters who go on to commit atrocities of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85420.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "Columbine was a tidal wave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88200.0,
      "end_time": 89276.0,
      "text": "and when the crash ended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89300.0,
      "end_time": 93235.0,
      "text": "it would take years for the community and for society"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 94980.0,
      "text": "to comprehend its impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96540.0,
      "end_time": 100660.0,
      "text": "It has taken me years to try to accept my son's legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101580.0,
      "end_time": 104716.0,
      "text": "The cruel behavior that defined the end of his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104740.0,
      "end_time": 108300.0,
      "text": "showed me that he was a completely different person from the one I knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109420.0,
      "end_time": 111796.0,
      "text": "Afterwards people asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111820.0,
      "end_time": 113580.0,
      "text": "\"How could you not know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114380.0,
      "end_time": 115940.0,
      "text": "What kind of a mother were you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117600.0,
      "end_time": 119700.0,
      "text": "I still ask myself those same questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120900.0,
      "end_time": 123780.0,
      "text": "Before the shootings, I thought of myself as a good mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 127360.0,
      "text": "Helping my children become caring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 129396.0,
      "text": "healthy, responsible adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129419.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132899.0,
      "text": "was the most important role of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133580.0,
      "end_time": 136900.0,
      "text": "But the tragedy convinced me that I failed as a parent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137660.0,
      "end_time": 141380.0,
      "text": "and it's partially this sense of failure that brings me here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143600.0,
      "end_time": 144316.0,
      "text": "Aside from his father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144340.0,
      "end_time": 147900.0,
      "text": "I was the one person who knew and loved Dylan the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148620.0,
      "end_time": 150876.0,
      "text": "If anyone could have known what was happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150900.0,
      "end_time": 152620.0,
      "text": "it should have been me, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153820.0,
      "end_time": 155190.0,
      "text": "But I didn't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159155.0,
      "text": "Today, I'm here to share the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159180.0,
      "end_time": 162900.0,
      "text": "of what it's like to be the mother of someone who kills and hurts."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 167876.0,
      "text": "For years after the tragedy, I combed through memories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167900.0,
      "end_time": 171500.0,
      "text": "trying to figure out exactly where I failed as a parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172100.0,
      "end_time": 174835.0,
      "text": "But there are no simple answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174860.0,
      "end_time": 176780.0,
      "text": "I can't give you any solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 177340.0,
      "end_time": 178540.0,
      "text": "All I can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179580.0,
      "end_time": 181940.0,
      "text": "is share what I have learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186876.0,
      "text": "When I talk to people who didn't know me before the shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186900.0,
      "end_time": 188700.0,
      "text": "I have three challenges to meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189460.0,
      "end_time": 192660.0,
      "text": "First, when I walk into a room like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 193300.0,
      "end_time": 196876.0,
      "text": "I never know if someone there has experienced loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196900.0,
      "end_time": 198620.0,
      "text": "because of what my son did."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 199900.0,
      "end_time": 204360.0,
      "text": "I feel a need to acknowledge the suffering caused by a member of my family"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204600.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "who isn't here to do it for himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206900.0,
      "end_time": 209460.0,
      "text": "So first, with all of my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210140.0,
      "end_time": 213380.0,
      "text": "I'm sorry if my son has caused you pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215460.0,
      "end_time": 217220.0,
      "text": "The second challenge I have"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217860.0,
      "end_time": 221580.0,
      "text": "is that I must ask for understanding and even compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222380.0,
      "end_time": 225620.0,
      "text": "when I talk about my son's death as a suicide."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226300.0,
      "end_time": 228436.0,
      "text": "Two years before he died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228460.0,
      "end_time": 230676.0,
      "text": "he wrote on a piece of paper in a notebook"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 230700.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "that he was cutting himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233200.0,
      "end_time": 234636.0,
      "text": "He said that he was in agony"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 234660.0,
      "end_time": 237299.0,
      "text": "and wanted to get a gun so he could end his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237980.0,
      "end_time": 241739.0,
      "text": "I didn't know about any of this until months after his death."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242540.0,
      "end_time": 245956.0,
      "text": "When I talk about his death as a suicide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245980.0,
      "end_time": 250190.0,
      "text": "I'm not trying to downplay the viciousness he showed at the end of his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 250660.0,
      "end_time": 252636.0,
      "text": "I'm trying to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 252660.0,
      "end_time": 254756.0,
      "text": "how his suicidal thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254780.0,
      "end_time": 256220.0,
      "text": "led to murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256899.0,
      "end_time": 260116.0,
      "text": "After a lot of reading and talking with experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260140.0,
      "end_time": 261796.0,
      "text": "I have come to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 261820.0,
      "end_time": 266540.0,
      "text": "that his involvement in the shootings was rooted not in his desire to kill"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267300.0,
      "end_time": 268980.0,
      "text": "but in his desire to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270140.0,
      "end_time": 275436.0,
      "text": "The third challenge I have when I talk about my son's murder-suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 275460.0,
      "end_time": 278380.0,
      "text": "is that I'm talking about mental health --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 279500.0,
      "end_time": 280716.0,
      "text": "excuse me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 280740.0,
      "end_time": 283356.0,
      "text": "is that I'm talking about mental health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283380.0,
      "end_time": 287556.0,
      "text": "or brain health, as I prefer to call it, because it's more concrete."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287580.0,
      "end_time": 291316.0,
      "text": "And in the same breath, I'm talking about violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 291340.0,
      "end_time": 294916.0,
      "text": "The last thing I want to do is to contribute to the misunderstanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294940.0,
      "end_time": 298156.0,
      "text": "that already exists around mental illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 298180.0,
      "end_time": 302956.0,
      "text": "Only a very small percent of those who have a mental illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 302980.0,
      "end_time": 305220.0,
      "text": "are violent toward other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 306620.0,
      "end_time": 309756.0,
      "text": "but of those who die by suicide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 309780.0,
      "end_time": 313996.0,
      "text": "it's estimated that about 75 to maybe more than 90 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 317419.0,
      "text": "have a diagnosable mental health condition of some kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 318500.0,
      "end_time": 319756.0,
      "text": "As you all know very well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 319780.0,
      "end_time": 322739.0,
      "text": "our mental health care system is not equipped to help everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 323820.0,
      "end_time": 326316.0,
      "text": "and not everyone with destructive thoughts"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 326340.0,
      "end_time": 328750.0,
      "text": "fits the criteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328100.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "for a specific diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331200.0,
      "end_time": 333360.0,
      "text": "Many who have ongoing feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 333600.0,
      "end_time": 336796.0,
      "text": "of fear or anger or hopelessness"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 336820.0,
      "end_time": 338700.0,
      "text": "are never assessed or treated."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339460.0,
      "end_time": 344990.0,
      "text": "Too often, they get our attention only if they reach a behavioral crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 345220.0,
      "end_time": 347276.0,
      "text": "If estimates are correct"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 347300.0,
      "end_time": 350236.0,
      "text": "that about one to two percent of all suicides"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352340.0,
      "text": "involves the murder of another person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 353900.0,
      "end_time": 357820.0,
      "text": "when suicide rates rise, as they are rising for some populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 358540.0,
      "end_time": 361220.0,
      "text": "the murder-suicide rates will rise as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 362340.0,
      "end_time": 367835.0,
      "text": "I wanted to understand what was going on in Dylan's mind prior to his death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 367860.0,
      "end_time": 371580.0,
      "text": "so I looked for answers from other survivors of suicide loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373460.0,
      "end_time": 377996.0,
      "text": "I did research and volunteered to help with fund-raising events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 378200.0,
      "end_time": 379796.0,
      "text": "and whenever I could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 379820.0,
      "end_time": 384316.0,
      "text": "I talked with those who had survived their own suicidal crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 384340.0,
      "end_time": 385539.0,
      "text": "or attempt."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 386660.0,
      "end_time": 388876.0,
      "text": "One of the most helpful conversations I had"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 388900.0,
      "end_time": 390356.0,
      "text": "was with a coworker"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 390380.0,
      "end_time": 392284.0,
      "text": "who overheard me talking to someone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 392309.0,
      "end_time": 393509.0,
      "text": "in my office cubicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 394580.0,
      "end_time": 397996.0,
      "text": "She heard me say that Dylan could not have loved me"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 398200.0,
      "end_time": 400780.0,
      "text": "if he could do something as horrible as he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 401820.0,
      "end_time": 403620.0,
      "text": "Later, when she found me alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404580.0,
      "end_time": 407360.0,
      "text": "she apologized for overhearing that conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 407600.0,
      "end_time": 408620.0,
      "text": "but told me that I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 409700.0,
      "end_time": 412316.0,
      "text": "She said that when she was a young, single mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 412340.0,
      "end_time": 413780.0,
      "text": "with three small children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 414420.0,
      "end_time": 419600.0,
      "text": "she became severely depressed and was hospitalized to keep her safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 419820.0,
      "end_time": 422116.0,
      "text": "At the time, she was certain"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 422140.0,
      "end_time": 425395.0,
      "text": "that her children would be better off if she died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 425420.0,
      "end_time": 427660.0,
      "text": "so she had made a plan to end her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 428700.0,
      "end_time": 432756.0,
      "text": "She assured me that a mother's love was the strongest bond on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 432780.0,
      "end_time": 435820.0,
      "text": "and that she loved her children more than anything in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 436460.0,
      "end_time": 438676.0,
      "text": "but because of her illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 438700.0,
      "end_time": 441539.0,
      "text": "she was sure that they would be better off without her."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 443500.0,
      "end_time": 445876.0,
      "text": "What she said and what I've learned from others"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 445900.0,
      "end_time": 450635.0,
      "text": "is that we do not make the so-called decision or choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 450660.0,
      "end_time": 452236.0,
      "text": "to die by suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 455116.0,
      "text": "in the same way that we choose what car to drive"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 455140.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "or where to go on a Saturday night."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 458180.0,
      "end_time": 461276.0,
      "text": "When someone is in an extremely suicidal state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 461300.0,
      "end_time": 465820.0,
      "text": "they are in a stage four medical health emergency."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 466500.0,
      "end_time": 470980.0,
      "text": "Their thinking is impaired and they've lost access to tools of self-governance."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 472140.0,
      "end_time": 475316.0,
      "text": "Even though they can make a plan and act with logic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 475340.0,
      "end_time": 479275.0,
      "text": "their sense of truth is distorted by a filter of pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 479300.0,
      "end_time": 481900.0,
      "text": "through which they interpret their reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 482700.0,
      "end_time": 486356.0,
      "text": "Some people can be very good at hiding this state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 486380.0,
      "end_time": 488740.0,
      "text": "and they often have good reasons for doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 490660.0,
      "end_time": 493836.0,
      "text": "Many of us have suicidal thoughts at some point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 493860.0,
      "end_time": 497356.0,
      "text": "but persistent, ongoing thoughts of suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 497380.0,
      "end_time": 499596.0,
      "text": "and devising a means to die"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 499620.0,
      "end_time": 501956.0,
      "text": "are symptoms of pathology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 501980.0,
      "end_time": 503876.0,
      "text": "and like many illnesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 503900.0,
      "end_time": 506659.0,
      "text": "the condition has to be recognized and treated"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 507340.0,
      "end_time": 508859.0,
      "text": "before a life is lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 510420.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "But my son's death was not purely a suicide."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 514200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515780.00000000006,
      "text": "It involved mass murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 516900.0,
      "end_time": 522780.0,
      "text": "I wanted to know how his suicidal thinking became homicidal."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 523740.0,
      "end_time": 526900.0,
      "text": "But research is sparse and there are no simple answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 528600.0,
      "end_time": 530978.0,
      "text": "Yes, he probably had ongoing depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 532499.0,
      "end_time": 538600.0,
      "text": "He had a personality that was perfectionistic and self-reliant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 538940.0,
      "end_time": 542700.0,
      "text": "and that made him less likely to seek help from others."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 543700.0,
      "end_time": 547156.0,
      "text": "He had experienced triggering events at the school"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 547180.0,
      "end_time": 552579.0,
      "text": "that left him feeling debased and humiliated and mad."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 553980.0,
      "end_time": 557236.0,
      "text": "And he had a complicated friendship"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 561596.0,
      "text": "with a boy who shared his feelings of rage and alienation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 561620.0,
      "end_time": 564716.0,
      "text": "and who was seriously disturbed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 564740.0,
      "end_time": 566620.0,
      "text": "controlling and homicidal."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 568100.0,
      "end_time": 570956.0,
      "text": "And on top of this period in his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 570980.0,
      "end_time": 574140.0,
      "text": "of extreme vulnerability and fragility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 575100.0,
      "end_time": 577476.0,
      "text": "Dylan found access to guns"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 577500.0,
      "end_time": 579660.0,
      "text": "even though we'd never owned any in our home."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 580620.0,
      "end_time": 585836.0,
      "text": "It was appallingly easy for a 17-year-old boy to buy guns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 585860.0,
      "end_time": 590500.0,
      "text": "both legally and illegally, without my permission or knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 591700.0,
      "end_time": 596220.0,
      "text": "And somehow, 17 years and many school shootings later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 596900.0,
      "end_time": 598699.0,
      "text": "it's still appallingly easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 600980.0,
      "end_time": 603700.0,
      "text": "What Dylan did that day broke my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 605600.0,
      "end_time": 606915.0,
      "text": "and as trauma so often does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 606940.0,
      "end_time": 609900.0,
      "text": "it took a toll on my body and on my mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 611180.0,
      "end_time": 613620.0,
      "text": "Two years after the shootings, I got breast cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 615200.0,
      "end_time": 618380.0,
      "text": "and two years after that, I began to have mental health problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 620300.0,
      "end_time": 623716.0,
      "text": "On top of the constant, perpetual grief"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 623740.0,
      "end_time": 627316.0,
      "text": "I was terrified that I would run into a family member"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 627340.0,
      "end_time": 629396.0,
      "text": "of someone Dylan had killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 629420.0,
      "end_time": 631795.0,
      "text": "or be accosted by the press"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 631820.0,
      "end_time": 633300.0,
      "text": "or by an angry citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 634740.0,
      "end_time": 637316.0,
      "text": "I was afraid to turn on the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 637340.0,
      "end_time": 642300.0,
      "text": "afraid to hear myself being called a terrible parent or a disgusting person."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 645140.0,
      "end_time": 647180.0,
      "text": "I started having panic attacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 649600.0,
      "end_time": 653236.0,
      "text": "The first bout started four years after the shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 655795.0,
      "text": "when I was getting ready for the depositions"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 655820.0,
      "end_time": 658620.0,
      "text": "and would have to meet the victims' families face to face."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 659420.0,
      "end_time": 662795.0,
      "text": "The second round started six years after the shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 662820.0,
      "end_time": 666276.0,
      "text": "when I was preparing to speak publicly about murder-suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 666300.0,
      "end_time": 668300.0,
      "text": "for the first time at a conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 669340.0,
      "end_time": 671740.0,
      "text": "Both episodes lasted several weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 673980.0,
      "end_time": 676116.0,
      "text": "The attacks happened everywhere:"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 676140.0,
      "end_time": 679436.0,
      "text": "in the hardware store, in my office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 679460.0,
      "end_time": 681500.0,
      "text": "or even while reading a book in bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 682420.0,
      "end_time": 687476.0,
      "text": "My mind would suddenly lock into this spinning cycle of terror"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 687500.0,
      "end_time": 689596.0,
      "text": "and no matter how I hard I tried"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 689620.0,
      "end_time": 693676.0,
      "text": "to calm myself down or reason my way out of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 693700.0,
      "end_time": 694980.0,
      "text": "I couldn't do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 698819.0,
      "text": "It felt as if my brain was trying to kill me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 699740.0,
      "end_time": 702316.0,
      "text": "and then, being afraid of being afraid"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 702340.0,
      "end_time": 704140.0,
      "text": "consumed all of my thoughts."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 705200.0,
      "end_time": 706915.0,
      "text": "That's when I learned firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 706940.0,
      "end_time": 709380.0,
      "text": "what it feels like to have a malfunctioning mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 710460.0,
      "end_time": 713940.0,
      "text": "and that's when I truly became a brain health advocate."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 715580.0,
      "end_time": 718556.0,
      "text": "With therapy and medication and self-care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 718580.0,
      "end_time": 720396.0,
      "text": "life eventually returned"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 720420.0,
      "end_time": 723900.0,
      "text": "to whatever could be thought of as normal under the circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 725600.0,
      "end_time": 727116.0,
      "text": "When I looked back on all that had happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 727140.0,
      "end_time": 730699.0,
      "text": "I could see that my son's spiral into dysfunction"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 731500.0,
      "end_time": 734996.0,
      "text": "probably occurred over a period of about two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 735200.0,
      "end_time": 737180.0,
      "text": "plenty of time to get him help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 738100.0,
      "end_time": 741116.0,
      "text": "if only someone had known that he needed help"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 741140.0,
      "end_time": 742460.0,
      "text": "and known what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 747500.0,
      "end_time": 750760.0,
      "text": "Every time someone asks me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 750100.0,
      "end_time": 752556.0,
      "text": "\"How could you not have known?\","
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 752580.0,
      "end_time": 754580.0,
      "text": "it feels like a punch in the gut."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 755660.0,
      "end_time": 760195.0,
      "text": "It carries accusation and taps into my feelings of guilt"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 760220.0,
      "end_time": 762716.0,
      "text": "that no matter how much therapy I've had"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 762740.0,
      "end_time": 764660.0,
      "text": "I will never fully eradicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 765700.0,
      "end_time": 767320.0,
      "text": "But here's something I've learned:"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 768540.0,
      "end_time": 770396.0,
      "text": "if love were enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 770420.0,
      "end_time": 772555.0,
      "text": "to stop someone who is suicidal"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 772580.0,
      "end_time": 774200.0,
      "text": "from hurting themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 774820.0,
      "end_time": 777200.0,
      "text": "suicides would hardly ever happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 778140.0,
      "end_time": 779939.0,
      "text": "But love is not enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 781600.0,
      "end_time": 782819.0,
      "text": "and suicide is prevalent."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 783500.0,
      "end_time": 786316.0,
      "text": "It's the second leading cause of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 786340.0,
      "end_time": 788540.0,
      "text": "for people age 10 to 34,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 789460.0,
      "end_time": 792116.0,
      "text": "and 15 percent of American youth"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 792140.0,
      "end_time": 794876.0,
      "text": "report having made a suicide plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 794900.0,
      "end_time": 796100.0,
      "text": "in the last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 797980.0,
      "end_time": 802100.0,
      "text": "I've learned that no matter how much we want to believe we can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 802820.0,
      "end_time": 805636.0,
      "text": "we cannot know or control"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 805660.0,
      "end_time": 807620.0,
      "text": "everything our loved ones think and feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 808580.0,
      "end_time": 811700.0,
      "text": "and the stubborn belief that we are somehow different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 812380.0,
      "end_time": 815796.0,
      "text": "that someone we love would never think of hurting themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 815820.0,
      "end_time": 817200.0,
      "text": "or someone else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 817900.0,
      "end_time": 819915.0,
      "text": "can cause us to miss"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 819940.0,
      "end_time": 821740.0,
      "text": "what's hidden in plain sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 823660.0,
      "end_time": 827100.0,
      "text": "And if worst case scenarios do come to pass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 828340.0,
      "end_time": 832236.0,
      "text": "we'll have to learn to forgive ourselves for not knowing"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 832260.0,
      "end_time": 834956.0,
      "text": "or for not asking the right questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 834980.0,
      "end_time": 837700.0,
      "text": "or not finding the right treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 839600.0,
      "end_time": 840315.0,
      "text": "We should always assume"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 840340.0,
      "end_time": 842980.0,
      "text": "that someone we love may be suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 843700.0,
      "end_time": 846316.0,
      "text": "regardless of what they say"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 846340.0,
      "end_time": 847580.0,
      "text": "or how they act."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 848540.0,
      "end_time": 850660.0,
      "text": "We should listen with our whole being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 851620.0,
      "end_time": 852820.0,
      "text": "without judgments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 853500.0,
      "end_time": 855620.0,
      "text": "and without offering solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 859180.0,
      "end_time": 862396.0,
      "text": "I know that I will live with this tragedy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 862420.0,
      "end_time": 864356.0,
      "text": "with these multiple tragedies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 864380.0,
      "end_time": 865939.0,
      "text": "for the rest of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 867140.0,
      "end_time": 869140.0,
      "text": "I know that in the minds of many,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 872900.0,
      "end_time": 876660.0,
      "text": "what I lost can't compare to what the other families lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 878600.0,
      "end_time": 880660.0,
      "text": "I know my struggle doesn't make theirs any easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 882820.0,
      "end_time": 888196.0,
      "text": "I know there are even some who think I don't have the right to any pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 888220.0,
      "end_time": 891600.0,
      "text": "but only to a life of permanent penance."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 893620.0,
      "end_time": 896300.0,
      "text": "In the end what I know comes down to this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 897140.0,
      "end_time": 903316.0,
      "text": "the tragic fact is that even the most vigilant and responsible of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 903340.0,
      "end_time": 905260.0,
      "text": "may not be able to help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 906660.0,
      "end_time": 908836.0,
      "text": "but for love's sake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 908860.0,
      "end_time": 911360.0,
      "text": "we must never stop trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 911600.0,
      "end_time": 912540.0,
      "text": "to know the unknowable."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 913380.0,
      "end_time": 914596.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 914620.0,
      "end_time": 916780.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}